name: Location
description: A geographic location
example: World, ..., Country, State, Country, City, Cruise ship

name: World
description: Top level location

name: UNRegion
description: Continental regions according to the M49 standard defined by the Statistics Division of the United Nations Secretariat

name: UNSubRegion
description: Subcontinental regions according to the M49 standard defined by the Statistics Division of the United Nations Secretariat

name: UNIntermediateRegion
description: Subdivisions of subcontinental regions according to the M49 standard defined by the Statistics Division of the United Nations Secretariat

name: Country
description: Countries and dependent Territories defined by ISO

name: Admin1
description: First administrative divisions, e.g, State, Province, Municipality

name: Admin2
description: Second administrative divisions: County in the US

name: City
description: City

name: PostalCode
description: E.g., a ZIP Code is a postal code used by the United States Postal Service (USPS)

name: Tract
description: Census tracts are small, relatively permanent statistical subdivisions of a county

name: Demographics
description: The statistical characterization of human populations or segments of human populations (e.g., characterization by age, sex, race, or income)

name: CruiseShip
description: Cruise ship

name: USRegion
description: Regions defined by the US Census Bureau

name: USDivision
description: Divisions defined by the US Census Burea

name: Cases
description: Number of case for outbreaks or diseases at specific dates and locations

name: Outbreak
description: Statistically significant increase in disease occurance in a community, population, or region

name: Organism
description: Individual living system, such as animal, plant, bacteria or virus, that is capable of replicating or reproducing, growth and maintenance in the right environment

name: Host
description: A host organism provides an environment supportive for the survival, growth, maturation, or reproduction of a virus

name: Pathogen
description: A bacterium, virus, or other microorganism that can cause disease

name: Strain
description: A population of organisms that is geneticaly different from others of the same species and possessing a set of defined characteristics

name: Clade
shortDescription: Group of organisms based on common ancestors
description: An identifier that denotes a group of organisms or groups of organisms based on common ancestors

name: Gene
description: Sequence of nucleotides in DNA or RNA that encodes the synthesis of a gene product, either RNA or protein

name: Variant
description: Natural sequence variants due to polymorphisms, disease-associated mutations, RNA editing and variations between strains, isolates or cultivars

name: Protein
description: Proteins are large biomolecules consisting of chains of amino acid residues

name: Publication
description: A document that has been accepted by a publisher

name: Demographics
description: Population statistics from the American Community Survey 5-year 2018 estimates

name: SocialCharacteristics
description: Social characteristics from the American Community Survey 5-year 2018 estimates

name: Education
description: Education attainment from the American Community Survey 5-year 2018 estimates

name: Computers
description: Households that use computers and internet from the American Community Survey 5-year 2018 estimates

name: Economics
description: Economic characteristics from the American Community Survey 5-year 2018 estimates

name: Commuting
description: Commuting to work from the American Community Survey 5-year 2018 estimates

name: Income
description: Household income from the American Community Survey 5-year 2018 estimates

name: Poverty
description: Families and people whose income in the past 12 month was below the poverty level

name: Employment
description: Employment status from the American Community Survey 5-year 2018 estimates

name: HealthInsurance
description: Health insurance coverage from the American Community Survey 5-year 2018 estimates

name: Occupation
description: Type of coccupation from the American Community Survey 5-year 2018 estimates

name: Housing
description: Housing characteristics from the American Community Survey 5-year 2018 estimates
